This directory contains optional AI features used by uhoh for local-only change summaries.

AI remains disabled by default. When enabled, uhoh can auto-download/update sidecar
binaries under `~/.uhoh/sidecar`, auto-download selected model files under
`~/.uhoh/models`, and (on Apple Silicon macOS) auto-manage an MLX virtualenv under
`~/.uhoh/venv/mlx`.

Inference backends:
- llama.cpp `llama-server` (preferred default backend)
- MLX (`mlx_lm.server`) on supported Apple Silicon macOS setups

Both backends are health-checked via `/v1/models` and run on loopback only.
